snippet.title: Deep Rock Galactic: Special Edition – PS5 Physical Edition Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Deep Rock Galactic: Special Edition for PlayStation 5 is now available!

Get your copy at https://deeprockgalactic.skybound.com

Deep Rock Galactic from Ghost Ship Games is a 1-4 player co-op FPS featuring badass space Dwarves, 100% destructible environments, procedurally-generated caves, and endless hordes of alien monsters.
